column5: :P:P:P thankyou misfish.  I posted this cuz i guess there was not enough snow in the previous picture....LOL........  We are in the south ya know and not the great white north.......lol   How ever i am bloody excited to get up there..Only four more day's......whooo.hoooo.....lol

Was thinking the same thing Brian........ "WHERE'S THE SNOW"...... Sometimes looks a lil diff through a forest i guess.... Looks like a blanket out here.....only prob tho, You dont even make a footprint in ours...shes ice on top Have a safe day...Im thinking on staying put today....not sure yet.

Lots of bad roads up this way, or so I'm told   I'm so happy it's another day off for me   The news does say the 400 is in bad shape, so if you venture out, be careful and remember, better late than never...  Maureen
The Hwy. I take to work is still closed due to nil visibility. Should have been at work over a hour ago. If it doesn't open soon, not worth going at all. May open after the suns up??
